translation[7]{c,v,t}:
  1,1,"Egameni lika-Allah, uNomusa, oSihawu"
  1,2,Udumo malube kuAllah umdali nomondli wemihlaba
  1,3,Onomusa onesihawu
  1,4,Umbusi welanga lokwahlulelwa
  1,5,Uwena (kuphela) esimkhonzayo futhi uwena kuphela esicela kuwe usizo
  1,6,Siholele endleleni eqondile
  1,7,Indlela yalabo obaphe umusa Hhayi (indlela) yalabo okwehliselwe ulaka phezulu kwabo nalabo abedukayo
